    "title": "Drunk Stoned Brilliant Dead: The Story of the National Lampoon",
    "updated": "2015-05-27 12:53:22",
    "description": "<p>From its beginnings as a humble university publication through to becoming the brand adorning films such as Animal House and the Vacation series, this compelling documentary charts the evolution of influential satirical magazine and American comedy institution, National Lampoon.  Featuring archive appearances and contributions from such luminaries as John Belushi, Gilda Radner, Bill Murray, Judd Apatow, Kevin Bacon, (see also Cop Car), John Landis, Chevy Chase, Billy Bob Thornton and John Goodman.<\/p>",
